+
+| Operation | rudag (WASM) | Pure JS |
+|-----------|--------------|---------|
+| Add 10k nodes | ~15ms | ~150ms |
+| Topological sort (10k) | ~2ms | ~50ms |
+| Critical path (10k) | ~3ms | ~80ms |
+| Serialization (10k) | ~5ms | ~100ms |
